title: Roosbeef - Ze willen wel je hond aaien, maar niet met je praten
description:
------------------------------------------------
Roosbeef is the performance name of Roos Rebergen, a girl grown up on a farm in the municipality of Duiven (wiki). Hence their first song was named Boerderij ('Farm') Firery red hair, remarkably witted and blessed with an entirely unique view toward all and everything, Roos does things in her own fashion. Noticably. She's a genre of her own. Is it cabaret art? According to her, it's not. Is it pop? She claims it is, but what does it matter? Call it what you will.
------------------------------------------------


Album (cd) released: 12 december 2008
